snippet.title: Letalis - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2396200/Letalis/

Letalis is a a non-linear RPG set in colosseums controlled by Caesars, where warriors fight for “Glory or Death”. Delve into a unique journey with over a thousand Letalis, each with their own fighting styles, quirks, and aesthetics.
